      {
        "start": 0.0,
        "duration": 11.1,
        "text": "Hi, friends. It's me, Baby Taco. Do you remember our last adventure? We met so many"
      },
      {
        "start": 11.1,
        "duration": 14.7,
        "text": "farm friends. Mr. Cow, Mrs. Chicken, Piggy, Ducky, Horsey, Sheepie, and more. But today,"
      },
      {
        "start": 25.8,
        "duration": 12.2,
        "text": "I hear something. Lots of funny sounds around the farm. Do you hear them, too? Let's play a guessing"
      },
      {
        "start": 38.1,
        "duration": 11.0,
        "text": "game. I'll play a sound. You listen carefully and we'll figure out who it is together. Are you"
      },
      {
        "start": 49.1,
        "duration": 6.2,
        "text": "ready, friends? Yay! Let's go!"
      },
      {
        "start": 60.9,
        "duration": 17.0,
        "text": "Oh, what's that sound? Glug, glug, glug. Hmm, is it bubbles? Is it rain? What do you think, friends?"
      },
      {
        "start": 80.1,
        "duration": 10.4,
        "text": "Uh-huh. It's the baby calf drinking milk from Mama Cow. Glug, glug, so yummy and healthy."
      },
      {
        "start": 92.5,
        "duration": 2.6,
        "text": "Can you pretend to drink milk with me?"
      },
      {
        "start": 102.1,
        "duration": 1.0,
        "text": "Delicious."
      },
      {
        "start": 109.1,
        "duration": 17.0,
        "text": "Uh-oh. I hear crunch, crunch, crunch. Is it someone eating cookies? Or maybe carrots?"
      },
      {
        "start": 126.6,
        "duration": 12.2,
        "text": "Yes. Look, it's Mr. Horsey munching on hay. Crunch, crunch. Let's pretend to munch like horses."
      },
      {
        "start": 140.0,
        "duration": 5.9,
        "text": "Ready? Crunch, crunch, crunch. Yay!"
      },
      {
        "start": 156.8,
        "duration": 8.4,
        "text": "Hmm, what's that? Flap, flap, flap. Is something flying?"
      },
      {
        "start": 169.9,
        "duration": 7.9,
        "text": "Oh, it's Mrs. Chicken shaking her wings. Can you flap your arms like little wings?"
      },
      {
        "start": 179.2,
        "duration": 5.0,
        "text": "Flap, flap, flap, flap, flap, flap, flap, flap, flap."
      },
      {
        "start": 186.3,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "Flap, flap, flap, flap, flap."
      },
      {
        "start": 191.3,
        "duration": 8.3,
        "text": "Ew. I hear something squishy. And wait. Oink, oink."
      },
      {
        "start": 203.3,
        "duration": 7.0,
        "text": "It's piggy-roin in the mud. Squish, squish, oink, oink, oink, oink, oink, oink, oink, oink, oink."
      },
      {
        "start": 210.4,
        "duration": 7.0,
        "text": "Stomp your feet like piggies in the mud. Stomp, stomp, splash. Wee!"
      },
      {
        "start": 227.9,
        "duration": 6.9,
        "text": "Snip, snip, ba, ba. Hmm. What's happening?"
      },
      {
        "start": 235.4,
