        "text": "Ba, ba, go, Shippy. Grab your teddy friends. Let's pretend to give them a tiny haircut."
      },
      {
        "start": 254.2,
        "duration": 5.1,
        "text": "Snip, snip, snip, ba, ba, ba."
      },
      {
        "start": 264.8,
        "duration": 10.1,
        "text": "Splish, splash, quack, quack. Who's playing in the pond?"
      },
      {
        "start": 276.4,
        "duration": 8.2,
        "text": "It's ducky and her little ducklings. Flap your arms, splash your feet, and quack with me."
      },
      {
        "start": 286.1,
