        "text": "Swish, swish, mool."
      },
      {
        "start": 325.8,
        "duration": 7.9,
        "text": "Thump, thump, thump. Naaaay. Sounds like someone's racing."
      },
      {
        "start": 335.0,
        "duration": 3.6,
        "text": "It's the baby horse galloping around the barn."
      },
      {
